#ROOMS
#100
Induction into Melee Magthere~
One thing that a child of the underdark learns early is the importance of 
station. Nothing, not even ones own life is more important. All for the glory
of the Spider Queen, and in the name of her glory shall you find your own
greatness. You find yourself within the walls of the Melee Magthere, school
of warriors, and the first school a child of valshara such as yourself is 
sent to. The brightest and most gifted in the mystical arts soon find their 
way to the Magthere D'Faern, while the most favored find themselves learning
the ways of the Spider Queen within the temple. Rumors of other paths exist,
but for now there is only one way, and that tis the path below you.
path before you.
~
0 4 13 0
D5
~
~
0 -1 101
S
#101
The Art of War~
The way of the drow is that of strife and chaos. To advance ones station,
one must be willing to strike down ones brothers and sisters. Through cunning
and intrigue rule the lives of the drow, there is always the impending threat
of attack from outside, under which all drow must unite and defend the savage
city they have carved from the caverns. For this reason, Melee Magthere exists.
For this reason you must pass the challenge before you now.
~
0 4 13 0
S
#102
Inn of the Melee Magthere~
You are within a large cavern deep within the stalgtite mound of the
Melee Magthere. Although rooms are paid for for nobles, most
chose instead to sleep in the common halls of the inn, since this way
they are less likely to be singled out for assassination. To the south,
you can hear the yelling and screaming of the slave pits.  The combat within
serves as entertainment to the drow.  To the west you can go to the teachers
within the school, while to the east there is a passage leading to the 
streets of valshara.
~
