#106
Entering the Torture Chambers~
Screams of pain an anguish bombard you in all directions as the students of
the Melee Magthere are given their introduction into the drow art of torture.
No other race can be as cruel without killing the victims.  The children
of Lloth have mastered the art of keeping one alive regardless of the 
pain and damage they inflict upon the body.  The bloodsoaked walls and 
broken bones that lie around belong not to the victims but rather to drow
that failed to keep the victim alive as they tortured them.
~
