that even here, Lloth watches her children and judges whether or not they 
are worthy of life. The greatest task before the drow is to wreak vengaence
upon the realms of the surface for casting them into the underdark in ages 
past. Without Lloths guidence, they surely would have fallen long ago. Only
through the glory of Lloth can one achieve greatness here, and it is her
will that all know the art of pain.
